an limit your operating hours to certain days of the week. Off-peak options are Wednesday and Thursday, Saturday and Sunday, and Monday and Friday. See details at pge.com/rateanalysis. Or call your agriculture advisor with questions at 1-877-311-3276, Monday-Friday, 7:00 a.m.-6:00 p.m.\n\nAGRICULTURE RATE PLANS *General guideline. Results may vary.\n\n",
